  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A letter from the Parliamentary Secretary General to all MPs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the third session of the Ninth Parliament is to be inaugurated by the President on 03 August 2022 at 10.30 am, Secretary General of the Parliament Mr. Dhammika Dasanayake has sent a letter to all MPs to attend the event.",
        "The Secretary General informs that the documents related to the commencement of the third session of the Ninth Parliament have already been uploaded on the official website of the Parliament (www.parlaiment.lk).",
        "Accordingly, the Special Gazette No. 2290/35 dated 2022.07.28 containing the announcement issued by the President concluding the second session of the Ninth Parliament, the agenda of the Parliament related to the ceremonial opening of the third session of the Ninth Parliament and the detailed note related to that date from the Parliament website. The Secretary General informs that it can be consulted."
      ],
